&CP2K
 PROGRAM      Quickstep
 PROJECT      H2S
 IOLEVEL      10
 FFTLIB       FFTSG
&END

&IO
 BASIS_SET_FILE BASIS_SET
 POTENTIAL_FILE POTENTIAL
&END

&DFT
 FUNCTIONAL   Pade
&END

&QS
 METHOD        GAPW
 CUTOFF        100
 NGRID        1
 EPS_GVG      1.0E-7
 EPS_PGF_ORB  1.0E-7
 QUADRATURE   GC_LOG
 EPSFIT       1.E-4
 EPSISO       1.0E-12
 EPSRHO0      1.E-4
 LMAXN0       4
 LMAXN1       6
 ALPHA0_H     10
 ALPHA0_S     1.83795571 
&END

&SCF
 GUESS        ATOMIC
 MAX_SCF      40
 EPS_SCF      1.0E-6
&END

&PRINT MEDIUM
&END

&KIND H
 BASIS_SET    DZVP-GTH-PADE
 POTENTIAL    GTH-BLYP-q1
&END

&KIND S
 BASIS_SET    DZVP-GTH-PADE
 POTENTIAL    GTH-BLYP-q6
&END

&CELL
 UNIT         ANGSTROM
 ABC          10.0  10.0  10.0
&END

&COORDS
 S       -0.00000       -0.05100        0.00000
  H       -1.03000        0.81300       -0.00000
  H        1.03000        0.81300       -0.00000
&END
